summary:
•	Certified Project Management Professional (PMP) Delivery Director with a proven track record of providing strategic leadership, implementing organizational change, and developing new business capabilities. Diverse roles played including delivery and program manager, product manager, head of department and location delivery head
•	Strong interpersonal and customer service skills able to manage and influence people, processes, and customer relationships, with a track record of managing and mentoring teams, developing business, and creating business relations with clients
•	Proved experience of digital transformation strategy implementation through integration of digital technology into all areas of a business, fundamentally changing how the company operates and delivers value to customers
•	Cross industry expertise with commercial acumen across Retail, Telco and Fintech sectors and consulting experience in international organizations with wide range of assignments covering key digital practice areas (eCommerce, mobile apps, digital marketing, etc.)
•	Enterprise Agile implementation experience including scaled agile SAFe
•	Background as Java software engineer, MSc in Applied Mathematics and Computer Science. Additional degrees in psychology and management. Fluent in English, Spanish and Russian.
